items.sentence: The guy I lent my umbrella to didn\'t return it.
I don\'t think we\'re going to need Tom\'s help.

Tom doesn\'t know where Mary buys her groceries.
Tom doesn\'t know whether to turn left or right.
Tom doesn\'t really want to go swimming with us.
Tom doesn\'t want to deal with this problem now.

If you want to get out of here alive, follow me.
